sequenceDiagram
    participant HS as Spark History Server
    participant Connector as HS Connector
    participant NATS
    participant Analyzer
    participant Gateway

    Note over Connector: asyncio background task<br/>triggers every N seconds

    Connector->>HS: list_applications(limit=batch_size)
    HS-->>Connector: [app_1, app_2, app_3]
    Connector->>Connector: filter via PollingState (skip processed)

    loop For each new app
        Connector->>HS: fetch 5 REST endpoints
        HS-->>Connector: raw data
        Connector->>Connector: map_job_analysis() → JobAnalysis
        Connector->>NATS: publish("analyze.request", JobAnalysis)
        Connector->>Connector: PollingState.mark_processed(app_id)
    end

    NATS->>Analyzer: deliver message(s)
    Analyzer->>Analyzer: 11 rules + optional AI analysis
    Analyzer->>NATS: publish("analyze.result", AnalysisResult)

    NATS->>Gateway: deliver to subscriber
    Gateway->>Gateway: store result
